comments: Covington (HOU) makes marginal contact with McCollum (POR) during the drive.
Tucker (HOU) moves into Nurkic's (POR) path and initiates lower body contact that affects his shot attempt.
Covington (HOU) extends his arm across Lillard's (POR) body and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Lillard (POR) legally contests Harden's (HOU) jump shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) maintains a legal guarding position on Harden (HOU) during the drive.
Covington (HOU) makes clean contact with the ball during the rebound to force a tie-up.
Tucker (POR) makes marginal contact with Trent Jr. (POR) before deflecting the loose ball away.
Harden (HOU) goes to not through Lillard's (POR) body before the shot attempt.
House Jr. (HOU) makes contact with Lillard's (POR) arm and affects his SQBR.
Lillard (POR) cleanly deflects the ball away from Covington (HOU).
After the pass attempt, Covington (HOU) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Lillard (POR).
While going for the rebound, Trent Jr. (POR) makes contact with the ball and brushes Westbrook's (HOU) arm in the process.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Lillard (POR).
Westbrook (HOU) commits a take foul on Anthony (POR).
Nurkic (POR) and Tucker (HOU) engage and separate during the rebound.
